{"title": "Final Report of the President's Task Force on 21st Century Policing", "description": "In light of recent events that have exposed rifts in the relationships between local police and the communities they protect and serve, on December 18, 2014, President Barack Obama signed an executive order establishing the Task Force on 21st Century Policing. The President charged the task force with identifying best practices and offering recommendations on how policing practices can promote effective crime reduction while building public trust.<br/><br/>The task force recommendations, each with action items, are organized around six main topic areas or \u201cpillars:\u201d Building Trust and Legitimacy, Policy and Oversight, Technology and Social Media, Community Policing and Crime Reduction, Officer Training and Education, and Officer Safety and Wellness. (From the Executive Summary)", "duration": 12330, "language": "English", "authors": [{"id": "13435", "name": " President's Task Force on 21st Century Policing"}], "coverArt": "https://archive.org/download/finalreport_21st_century_policing_1809_librivox/final_report_president_1809.jpg", "copyright_year": "2015", "genres": ["Social Science (Culture & Anthropology)"], "supporters": [{"role": "Read by", "name": "LibriVox Volunteers"}, {"role": "Book Coordinator", "name": "TriciaG"}, {"role": "Meta Coordinator", "name": "TriciaG"}, {"role": "Proof Listener", "name": "TriciaG"}], "sections": [{"section": 0, "title": "Prefatory Material, Executive Summary", "readers": [23], "path": "http://www.archive.org/download/finalreport_21st_century_policing_1809_librivox/21stcenturypolicing_00_taskforce_64kb.mp3", "duration": 1295}, {"section": 1, "title": "Introduction", "readers": [11528], "path": "http://www.archive.org/download/finalreport_21st_century_policing_1809_librivox/21stcenturypolicing_01_taskforce_64kb.mp3", "duration": 807}, {"section": 2, "title": "Pillar 1. Building Trust and Legitimacy, part 1", "readers": [11715],